    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/3a6d9673c8b4636194f6f1c9ca38a954.poster.avif?t=1765347921\" width=612 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/3a6d9673c8b4636194f6f1c9ca38a954.webm?t=1765347921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/3a6d9673c8b4636194f6f1c9ca38a954.mp4?t=1765347921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aleph是一款由四个超现实场景构成的短篇实验作品，围绕 [屏幕] 与 [方块] 两个要素，展现未来人类收集散落于各处的旧日知识碎片的一段旅途</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 轻松的第一人称探索体验，搭配一定的收集要素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 友好的操作提示，支持手柄，可以帮助新玩家熟悉主视角游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 舒缓的节奏和低难度的挑战，适合所有年龄层</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 贯穿全程的多首长氛围音乐，阅读并聆听经典著作的节选段落</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 精简的流程，约45分钟的通关时长</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/3d7a8459782358919e81bfcaf7188d56.poster.avif?t=1765347921\" width=612 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/3d7a8459782358919e81bfcaf7188d56.webm?t=1765347921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/3d7a8459782358919e81bfcaf7188d56.mp4?t=1765347921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作品聚焦并发展自虚拟展厅这一概念</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >早期版本曾多次在美术馆的线下展览中展出，并从中获得新的启发与完善...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/25f230a54b520e7da9d1b48c94c92df9.poster.avif?t=1765347921\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/25f230a54b520e7da9d1b48c94c92df9.webm?t=1765347921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387410/extras/25f230a54b520e7da9d1b48c94c92df9.mp4?t=1765347921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Credits]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 作者:   刘豪格  、钽坦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 图形设计:  力凡 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 音乐 &amp; 音效设计:  suru</p>",
